dataset.title: Taungurungia gen. nov., from the Lower Devonian of Yea, central Victoria, Australia

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article McSweeney, Fearghus R., Shimeta, Jeff, Buckeridge, John St J. S.
